title: Hour 3 - Michael Strahan
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Michael Strahan
description:
On this edition of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan is joined by NFL HoF DE Michael Strahan to talk about his career, the current crop of edge rushers, and his post-playing career.
